    <bp:comment rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Platelet releasate contains a range of proteins that do not originate in specialized storage granules. In some cases platelet lysis may  contribute to the presence of these proteins in the platelet relesate.</bp:comment>
